title: Brandon 2-month Trial Period
body:
Greetings y'all 👋 This proposal is for kicking off my 2-month trial period as a full-time contributor to R Group.

Like the rest of the DAO, we're just getting things started, but have reached consensus on a high-level set of processes, including our approach to contributor onboarding and compensation guidelines:
 
* [R Group Structure, Goals, & Processes](shttps://docs.google.com/document/d/1TxkoelIV7HV5kV6yn30id6EY3hv7i-j-JvJ-HvNxeB4/edit?usp=sharing)

I wanted to clearly capture how I aim to contribute,  my technical background and skillset, and the ways in which I will hold myself publicly accountable:

* [Brandon @ Rarible DAO - Contribution](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fxf-LSVjBO5qnZ-4Z5q5a0vhL8eCBgbDXjwnsZfun80/edit?usp=sharing)

The breakdown of my proposed compensation per our WG guidelines and my rationale is provided here:

* [Brandon @ Rarible DAO - Compensation](https://docs.google.com/document/d/11xUTqwLjppxXkTNOs-4AHIlA6_1VFQSHsXszoQy7iAs/edit?usp=sharing)

I look forward to building with y'all!
author: 0x303EeFeDeE1bA8e5d507a55465d946B2fea18583
